it was responsible for all my best ideas?

545
00:40:47,333 --> 00:40:50,211
Have you ever been to Florida?

546
00:40:50,253 --> 00:40:51,845
No.

547
00:40:51,893 --> 00:40:53,884
You would like Key West.

548
00:40:53,933 --> 00:40:57,050
- Hemingway lived there.
