00:42:05,493 --> 00:42:09,202
My God, what a mess that'd make!

568
00:42:20,053 --> 00:42:22,647
- Hey, pretty good night.
- Yeah.

569
00:42:22,693 --> 00:42:26,891
Wait till the weekend
after all the college kids get back.

570
00:42:26,933 --> 00:42:31,529
I'm not 100% sure we got our costs in line
on the new menu, but...

571
00:42:32,333 --> 00:42:34,324
