586
00:43:31,733 --> 00:43:35,123
used books upstairs,
a nice little cottage out back.

587
00:43:42,493 --> 00:43:44,688
- And?
- What?

588
00:43:44,733 --> 00:43:46,928
How much was it?

589
00:43:48,133 --> 00:43:53,969
Look, I can't make snap decisions like you do.
OK? I've got Tick to think about.

590
00:43:54,013 --> 00:43:58,291
I must've been doing 100 when I ploughed
