what she wanted me to do before she died.

615
00:45:36,973 --> 00:45:38,770
Yeah, what was that?

616
00:45:38,813 --> 00:45:42,283
She said, "David, look after your brother."

617
00:45:44,893 --> 00:45:48,090
- She didn't say that.
- She did say that.

618
00:45:49,333 --> 00:45:52,052
Why don't you take the wheel, Miles?

619
00:45:55,133 --> 00:45:58,603
