630
00:46:49,093 --> 00:46:51,527
Honestly, Father Tom!

631
00:46:59,093 --> 00:47:01,084
<i>Or justice?</i>

632
00:47:07,773 --> 00:47:09,764
<i>Or release?</i>

633
00:47:12,493 --> 00:47:14,688
<i>Or an end to care?</i>

634
00:47:43,613 --> 00:47:45,683
<i>Lives are like rivers.</i>

635
00:47:45,733 --> 00:47:48,452
<i>Eventually they go where they must,</i>

636
00:47:49,453 --> 00:47:51,648
<i>not where we want them to.</i>

637
00:48:35,253 --> 00:48:38,370
Cindy, I had no idea you were home.

638
00:48:38,413 --> 00:48:41,371
I so wanted to surprise you and I have,
