639
00:48:41,413 --> 00:48:43,449
Let me have a look at you.

640
00:48:44,693 --> 00:48:46,684
You look great.

641
00:48:48,373 --> 00:48:49,772
- You OK?
- Yeah.

642
00:48:49,813 --> 00:48:51,804
Take it easy.

643
00:48:52,573 --> 00:48:55,292
So how are you?

644
00:48:55,333 --> 00:48:58,370
Well, Miles, I'm so, so well.

645
00:48:58,413 --> 00:49:00,608
The doctors are amazed.

646
00:49:00,653 --> 00:49:02,962
I haven't had any setbacks in...

647
00:49:04,413 --> 00:49:06,449
so long.

648
00:49:06,493 --> 00:49:10,725
It seems I'm to begin life again
as a normal person.

649
00:49:10,773 --> 00:49:14,243
- You can congratulate me.
- That's wonderful, Cindy.

650
00:49:15,453 --> 00:49:17,842
<i>Cindy Whiting.</i>

651
00:49:17,893 --> 00:49:21,647
<i>She'd been only three</i>
<i>when she was run over outside their home,</i>

652
00:49:21,693 --> 00:49:23,684
<i>the driver never apprehended.</i>

653
00:49:23,733 --> 00:49:26,725
<i>One desperate heartbreaking operation</i>
<i>after another</i>

654
00:49:26,773 --> 00:49:31,927
