Just until I find a place of my own.

656
00:49:37,773 --> 00:49:41,607
A grown woman needs a place
to come and go as she pleases

657
00:49:41,653 --> 00:49:44,884
and entertain whom she pleases.

658
00:49:46,773 --> 00:49:48,206
